457
01:04:12,019 --> 01:04:14,010
- So?
- Sir?

458
01:04:14,121 --> 01:04:18,285
- Should I continue?
- Please do.

459
01:04:18,392 --> 01:04:20,884
I lost my enthusiasm...

460
